{"type": "article", "id": 14055, "title": "树蜡笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606001459I2L90iP48jhuzDlN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t蜡笔在使用时包装纸很容易脱落，这盒蜡笔索性去掉了包装纸，模拟了树干凹凸不平的外形。设计者阿邓称，他的蜡笔源于台北市里不同的树，颜色也来自于树叶和花瓣。同时，他用冷暖两种色系将蜡笔装在不同的纸盒里，盒子外配上了对应颜色弹性带子。浓厚的文艺气实在令人爱不释手。这样简单的设计在筹资网站上筹得超过2百万美元。计划在今年十一月出售。<a href=\"http://cms.qdaily.com/manager/articles/14045/www.zeczec.com/projects/treecrayon\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看相关信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261417014TohSMKjy7kEYvOx.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"745\" title=\"6\" alt=\"6\" data-ratio=\"0.93125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141702BjO9kKIg4a5vzfZY.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" title=\"6\" alt=\"6\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141702BAM6ErZQunPoYKIj.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"591\" title=\"6\" alt=\"6\" data-ratio=\"0.73875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}